{
  "texts": [
    "Applying CNN's attention mechanisms can enhance performance [50].",
    "Attention mechanisms contribute to improved feature extraction and performance in CNNs [51].",
    "Reference [52] introduced the Squeeze and Excitation (SE) module, which enhances model performance by adjusting the weights of feature maps.",
    "Reference [53] proposed an enhanced YOLOv5-based method that introduced the Convolutional Block Attention Module into the Neck network.",
    "The module enhances the characterization of target features by assigning weights that weaken the ability to extract features from complex backgrounds, thus improving the accuracy and efficiency of helmet detection in complex working environments."
  ]
}